unittitle_ssm: Manufacturers' Association of New York annual banquet programs
abstract_ssm: This collection contains two items from the Manufacturers' Association of New York: a program for the Association's 15th annual banquet held at the Union League Club in Brooklyn, dated 1908. The program includes a seating chart and a list of diners. Also included is a program for the 16th annual banquet held at the Brooklyn Academy of Music, 1909.
